<p><strong>Exam-related sentences:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>明天有考试，我要复习。(Míngtiān yǒu kǎoshì, wǒ yào fùxí.) — There's an exam tomorrow, I need to review.</li>
  <li>我考了九十分。(Wǒ kǎo le jiǔshí fēn.) — I scored 90 points.</li>
  <li>这次考试很难。(Zhè cì kǎoshì hěn nán.) — This exam was very hard.</li>
</ul>

