<p><strong>Online class phrases:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>老师，我听不到你的声音。(Lǎoshī, wǒ tīng bú dào nǐ de shēngyīn.) — Teacher, I can't hear you.</li>
  <li>请打开麦克风。(Qǐng dǎkāi màikèfēng.) — Please turn on your microphone.</li>
  <li>网络不好，我重新连一下。(Wǎngluò bù hǎo, wǒ chóngxīn lián yīxià.) — Bad connection, let me reconnect.</li>
</ul>

